{"id":281249,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/【图说天朝】大师在民间/","date":"2013-02-27T13:54:52Z","modified":"2013-02-27T13:54:53Z","title":"【图说天朝】大师在民间","content":"<p>“2013年，你缺什么？”近日央视多路记者街头采访，向路人询问“你缺什么”的问题，被访路人也是各种&#8221;神回复&#8221;，或引人捧腹，或发人深思，例如“缺钱”、“缺爱”、“缺水表”、“缺家庭团圆”&#8230;&#8230;据统计，&#8221;缺钱&#8221;在众多回答中中标率最高。图为其中有一名受访老大爷给出了充满哲理的回答：“所有的缺与不缺都是一种妄想”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/%e3%80%90%e5%9b%be%e8%af%b4%e5%a4%a9%e6%9c%9d%e3%80%91%e5%a4%a7%e5%b8%88%e5%9c%a8%e6%b0%91%e9%97%b4/attachment/82177075/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-281250\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-281250 aligncenter\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/82177075.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"363\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/82177075.png 550w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/02/82177075-300x197.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"> 视频<a href=\"http://my.tv.sohu.com/us/136886249/52519798.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">地址</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\n","author":1015,"categories":[18269,10466,21627,13770],"tags":[22395,9149,22394]}